metadata.name: врятувати україну
metadata.description:
врятувати україну - (Save Ukraine) 
I dedicate this artwork to the brave men and women fighting for their freedom in Ukraine. The truth is, there has not been a day I have not thought about your struggle, and your defiance in the face of aggression. Long live Ukraine. 
Original photography combined with digital processes in Procreate. 
Crypto Art NFT.
